//prescaler; sets the rate at which the fsm is run
always @(posedge up_clk) begin
  if (up_resetn  == 1'b0) begin
    presc_reg <= 'h0;
  end else begin
    if (presc_reg == 'h8000) begin
      presc_reg <= 'h0;
    end else begin
      presc_reg <= presc_reg + 1'b1;
    end
  end
end
